    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;HTTP has been in use by the World-Wide Web global information initiative since 1990.  This specification defines the protocol referred to as "HTTP/1.1", and is an update to RFC 2068. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
